CatDescriptText: David L. Lawrence was Mayor of the City of Pittsburgh 1946-1959, Governor of Pennsylvania 1959-1963, and he died in 1966.
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of three men clasping or shaking hands, including Melvin Peters on left and Pittsburgh Mayor David L. Lawrence in center, other men, including police officer in background, gathered in Office of the Mayor, City County Building
